en_822283_0	An awareness programme on ‘Human Immune Deficiency Virus and Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome’ (HIV & AIDS) was organized by the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi, on the directions of the Commander, Security Forces-Kilinochchi, Major General Vijitha Ravipriya on Monday (9) at the Nelumpiyasa Auditorium.
en_822283_1	This awareness lecture was conducted coincident with the ‘World AIDS Day’.
en_822283_2	More than 700 Army personnel including Officers listened to the lecture.
en_822283_3	Consultant Venerealogist Dr Chathurika Wickramarathna of the District Hospital, Kilinochchi conducted the awareness programme.
